ge fund managers?</p><p> SEIDES: I think it&#39;s always fair to say you believe, Barry, part of your belief system is that a hedge fund is supposed to capture these moves in markets.</p><p> RITHOLTZ: Some of them, one would think, right?</p><p> SEIDES: I&#39;m sure some of them did and some of them didn&#39;t. So you&#39;re talking about an average of a large number.</p><p> RITHOLTZ: Sure.</p><p> SEIDES: I would say that&#39;s not really part of my belief system of what a hedge fund is trying to deliver. It&#39;s much more about security selection and a relatively static portfolio construction. So I think that argument is very valid in those couple of years, 2009, 2010 probably, maybe 2011, which was a tough year for hedge funds.</p><p> You still had 2012 to 2017 to finish the bet.</p><p> RITHOLTZ: Right.</p><p> SEIDES: And that was just the market, what we&#39;ve seen in tech stocks. It was just a very, very hard index to beat, no matter what you were doing.</p><p> RITHOLTZ: So here&#39;s the lesson I learned from your bet, because I was very, alternatives are too expensive, everything is pricey, these guys all eventually underperform. But I&#39;ve evolved that view over time to, “Hey, if you could get into the top decile.”正确的？ I once was speaking somewhere and trashing hedge funds and someone said, “I have an allocation that I inherited from my father in DE Shaw. Are you telling me I should sell that?”</p><p> And my answer was, “Absolutely not.”如果你在，从顶部的列表往下看，我不知道，11,000 家对冲基金中的 100 家，阿尔法生成器，挑战是中位数与你在耶鲁大学时有 500 家的经历有很大不同对冲基金和 500 个 alpha 生成器。</p><p> SEIDES：是的，随着资本的增加，事情变得更加困难。</p><p>但你必须记住，你在指数中看到的往往是等权重的。根据定义，投资者的经验是资产加权。</p><p>因此，机构投资者将资金投入对冲基金的地方是 DE Shaw。是和千禧年在一起的。它与 Citadel 一起。这些公司继续产生所谓的“阿尔法”超额回报。这就是为什么当人们对“哦，对冲基金指数做到了这一点”进行如此多的审查时，这些资产仍然保留下来，称之为资产类别或策略。每个对冲基金指数都是等权重，但这不是投资者的经验。</p><p> RITHOLTZ：我已经向你的立场发展，因为我对这个行业的批评结果是有人对我说，“你知道，你实际上是在批评这个行业最底层的 90%。”我想，好吧，这是对我的批评的公平批评。如果你在任何事情上都处于前 10%，那么，上帝保佑，请留在那儿。但如果你没有选择更好的选择之一，那么你到底要付出什么代价才是真正的问题。我认为这就是巴菲特赌注的潜在一面，以及他